description: Nana's Heavenly Ice Cream Truck is San Diego's Newest Old School Ice Cream Truck.What a fun surprise to have an ice cream truck visit your child’s birthday party or make an adult feel like a child again! Enjoy our standard products from Good Humor, Popsicle & Blue Bunny .Corporate and Community Events, School Activities & FundraisersLet us be your “full-service” vendor at your next Expo, Trade Show, Parade, Festival, or Sports Event!Would you like a Nana's Heavenly Ice Cream truck to make an occasional visit to your place of work at lunchtime, to your company picnic, or just to reward your employees for a job well done?Are you planning an Ice Cream Social for your school or daycare center? Nana’s is sure to bring a smile to every child's face.Does your organization need to raise money? Talk to us about the opportunities!A Nana’s Heavenly Ice Cream truck is a “one-stop” concession service catering to the public of all ages.We'd love to make your next party a memorable success.
name: Nana's Heavenly Ice Cream Truck
